WEBVTT


00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:01.320
let me tell you about my mother in law

00:00:01.321 --> 00:00:03.240
this woman has no chill about her

00:00:03.241 --> 00:00:04.440
she is always on the go

00:00:04.441 --> 00:00:06.960
always doing something and is always down for an adventure

00:00:06.961 --> 00:00:07.960
and I think quite honestly

00:00:07.961 --> 00:00:10.540
she is my kids and his excuse to have adventures

00:00:10.560 --> 00:00:12.080
and so today is my son's sixth birthday

00:00:12.081 --> 00:00:14.840
it also happens to be the grand opening of the Great Wolfage in Naples

00:00:14.841 --> 00:00:18.120
which is where we live and so instead of just having a normal sleepover tonight

00:00:18.121 --> 00:00:20.620
like they do on any given day of the week

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:23.480
she decides it's best to book a suite at the Great Wolf Lodge

00:00:23.481 --> 00:00:25.060
to celebrate his sixth birthday

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:29.440
yeah so instead of just having a casual movie night at home

00:00:29.441 --> 00:00:31.980
they're gonna go party and swim at the indoor water park

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:35.100
it's fine it's fine

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:37.000
and I could be upset

00:00:37.001 --> 00:00:39.440
because she's taking them to do an experience that I don't get to be a part of

00:00:39.441 --> 00:00:41.640
but instead I think about the memories that my kids get to make with them

00:00:41.641 --> 00:00:42.880
and that they get to do something fun

00:00:42.881 --> 00:00:44.760
and it's going to be a birthday that he's always gonna remember

00:00:44.761 --> 00:00:46.220
and that is what it matters
